58b43-c8e0-454f-8486-2e2a30d4fd0b?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZ=
jmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ], Base wants to expand the talent pool by simpli=
