won=E2=80=99t have to worry about power outages, because when the power goe=
s down on the grid, the battery will just take over. (Seeing your neighbor=
=E2=80=99s power on while yours is off during an outage is great word of mo=
uth marketing, too).=C2=A0
Less obviously, but as importantly, the battery means that Base can offer c=
