risk with financial instruments for which they pay a premium.=C2=A0
=E2=80=9CThe hedge is a financial battery,=E2=80=9D as Jared described it. =
=E2=80=9CThe battery is a technical hedge.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0
Since Base can hedge with technology instead of options, it can pass the sa=
