aft, the company tweeted that it looked forward to &#8220;delivering CCAs <=
/span><strong>on schedule, within budget, and at scale</strong><span>.&#822=
1; Justin&#8217;s team laid the groundwork for that three-part promise.&#16=
0;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-heig=
ht: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">By the time he met Zach in late 2022, though=
, Justin was starting to get The Itch. His dad was an entrepreneur &#8211; =
he ran his own construction company in Detroit &#8211; and Justin wanted to=
 start his own thing too. But what was big enough to work on after SpaceX a=
nd Anduril?&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; l=
ine-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">He thought about the question, like =
he thinks about most problems, as an engineer.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: =
rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">G=
DP per Capita is the best measure of human prosperity. How do you move it?&=
#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: =
