on capabilities, local weather conditions, and demand profiles. Texas is al=
l on its own.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px;=
 line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">A grid is a tricky thing to manage=
